# ./db/<name>/ — RocksDB / rocksdict stores
# Track data + catalog files: *.sst, CURRENT, MANIFEST-*, OPTIONS-*, IDENTITY, rocksdict-config.json
# Ignore only runtime / machine-local noise (do NOT ignore *.sst):
db/**/LOCK
db/**/LOG
db/**/LOG.old.*
db/**/*.log
# Legacy SQLite files at db root
db/*.db
